 <span data-ttu-id="e40cb-256">下面的示例创建<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry>为 Active Directory 域服务中的节点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e40cb-256">The following example creates a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> for the node in the Active Directory Domain Services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e40cb-257">然后，它显示<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A>和<xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A>及其子节点的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e40cb-257">It then displays the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> properties of its child nodes.</span></span>  
  
